{"id":923955327,"question_id":10,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 2 months","timestamp":1680054759,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"1470 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/923955327/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Regular Expression Matching","memory":"42.9 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public boolean isMatch(String s, String p) {\n        \n        if(p.length()==0) return s.length()==0;\n        \n        boolean firstMatch = s.length()>0 && (s.charAt(0)==p.charAt(0) || p.charAt(0)=='.');\n        \n        if(p.length()>=2 && p.charAt(1)=='*'){\n            return isMatch(s, p.substring(2)) || (firstMatch && isMatch(s.substring(1), p));\n        }else{\n            \n            return firstMatch && isMatch(s.substring(1), p.substring(1));\n            \n        }\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"regular-expression-matching","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
